; This has been extracted from
; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/dos/boot.md

% boot, dos

# Boot from floppy image
BOOT <path_to_floppy_img>

# Boot from hard disk image
BOOT <path_to_hard_disk_img>

# Boot multiple floppy images
BOOT {{path/to/floppy1.img path/to/floppy2.img ...}}
